    "modeling_rules": [
      "The local LM sample actuator is represented with the exact writable fields and telemetry fields observed in experiments/experiment_data.",
      "Other Belimo actuators are represented at product-family level using current official catalog data and simplified writable surfaces that still match realistic HVAC use.",
      "Belimo sensors are measurement-only in the concept: they emit values but expose no writable settings through the sandbox API.",
      "Non-Belimo source equipment is simplified to the minimum writable controls needed to produce physically plausible hot/cold supply air and to exercise the same backend pipeline that a real building would use.",
      "Sandbox v1 uses a packaged rooftop heat-pump unit as the primary air source; air-cooled chiller and condensing boiler objects are included as catalog items for the later central-plant expansion path."
